#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:1557
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DROPPOINT_PIRATE_RAID_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You skirt around the edge of the depot, looking for any remaining loot. "
"Though the pirates took all of the weapons and armor, quite a few resources "
"remain."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:1564
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DROPPOINT_FORTIFICATIONS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Nearby are some Federation fortifications that have taken heavy damage. A "
"couple workers are busy trying to patch up the damage."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:1566
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DROPPOINT_FORTIFICATIONS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Hail and ask if they need any assistance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:1568
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DROPPOINT_FORTIFICATIONS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Any help you could offer would be a life saver. We only just barely "
"managed to chase away those damn Rebels, and they'll no doubt be returning "
"with reinforcements soon. We're undermanned and we won't be able to get "
"these repairs done in time.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:1570
