msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_CREW\"]/event[1]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew take some time experimenting and working with the faulty shield "
"generator. Eventually, they're able to get to the root of the problem, much "
"to the Zoltan's delight. \"All systems are nominal... Great! It should come "
"back on once we jump. Thanks for the help.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2094
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_CREW\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew take some time experimenting and working with the faulty shield "
"generator. While they don't get it working, they manage to diagnose it. "
"\"Well, I guess it's better than nothing... Now we know what's wrong.\" They"
" give you a small reward."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2098
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_CREW\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew take some time experimenting and working with the faulty shield "
"generator. It momentarily comes to life, then pops. Seems like they only got"
" it partially working. \"Well, I guess it's better than nothing... Maybe we "
"can make do with this for now.\" They give you a modest reward."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_CREW\"]/event[4]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew take some time experimenting and working with the faulty shield "
"generator. As one of your crew adjusts something, the generator pops and "
"burns before catching fire. Seems like you completely broke it. \"Way to go,"
" jackass. Now we're completely screwed.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2105
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_CREW\"]/event[5]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew take some time experimenting and working with the faulty shield "
"generator. Try as they might, they have absolutely no idea what's wrong with"
" it. The Zoltans shake their heads. \"How did you think you would know what "
"was wrong if we couldn't figure it out...?\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2110
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_REPAIR\"]/event[1]/text"
