"Your drone begins to tinker with the broken shield generator. Before too "
"long, the drone identifies the problem and the generator comes to life. "
"\"All systems are nominal... Great! It should come back on once we jump. "
"Thanks for the help.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2117
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_REPAIR\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your drone begins to tinker with the broken shield generator. It returns a "
"report saying that there is insufficient resources to repair, but prints a "
"readout of how it could be repaired. \"Well, I guess it's better than "
"nothing... Now we know what's wrong.\" They give you a small reward."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2124
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//eventList[@name=\"S1_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_SEND_REPAIR\"]/event[3]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your drone begins to tinker with the broken shield generator. It momentarily"
" comes to life, then pops. The drone prints a readout of the problems that "
"it identified but couldn't fix. \"Well, I guess it's better than nothing... "
"Maybe we can make do with this for now.\" They give you a modest reward."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2134
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_DROPPOINT_HAZARDOUS_FACILITY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A station at this beacon has alarms going off, and a distress call is out to"
" save the civilians on board. However, when you arrive, there's already a "
"Federation ship at the location, which hails you. \"No worries, we have the "
"situation under control. There was a hazardous chemical leak that "
"proliferated into the station's life support. We have already evacuated this"
" station; it looks like everyone's okay, but we have a civilian on board who"
" wishes to make a request.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2137
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_DROPPOINT_HAZARDOUS_FACILITY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Hear them out."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2139
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_DROPPOINT_HAZARDOUS_FACILITY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The civilian gets onto the comm. \"Ah, hello. I'm a merchant who trades with"
" this station. My ship is fortunately unharmed, but still docked - "
"unfortunately, the toxins have contaminated everything, so I can't undock it"
" myself. If you could steer my ship away and vent the atmosphere, it would "
"likely be safe for me to use it again. It's not quite as contaminated as the"
" station, but you probably won't survive if you aren't careful.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_droppoint.xml:2141
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_droppoint.xml$//event[@name=\"DISTRESS_DROPPOINT_HAZARDOUS_FACILITY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_NO2\"]/text"
